const formDataRadio = [
  {
    labelName: 'Arcade',
    typeInput: 'radio',
    value: 9,
    id: 'arcade',
    labelSpan: '$90/yr',
    labelSpan: '$90/yr',
    spanClass: 'text-[14px] font-normal text-grey',
    labelClass:
      'flex flex-col justify-end gap-[7px] text-[16px] text-denim font-medium w-[138px] h-[160px] rounded-[8px] border-[1px] border-[#D6D9E6] p-[16px] bg-arcade bg-no-repeat bg-[left_16px_top_20px] hover:border-[#483EFF] cursor-pointer',
  },
  {
    labelName: 'Advanced',
    typeInput: 'radio',
    value: 12,
    id: 'advanced',
    labelSpan: '$120/yr',
    spanClass: 'text-[14px] font-normal text-grey',
    labelClass:
      'flex flex-col justify-end gap-[7px] text-[16px] text-denim font-medium w-[138px] h-[160px] rounded-[8px] border-[1px] border-[#D6D9E6] p-[16px] bg-advanced bg-no-repeat bg-[left_16px_top_20px] hover:border-[#483EFF] cursor-pointer',
  },
  {
    labelName: 'Pro',
    typeInput: 'radio',
    value: 15,
    id: 'pro',
    labelSpan: '$150/yr',
    spanClass: 'text-[14px] font-normal text-grey',
    labelClass:
      'flex flex-col justify-end gap-[7px] text-[16px] text-denim font-medium w-[138px] h-[160px] rounded-[8px] border-[1px] border-[#D6D9E6] p-[16px] bg-pro bg-no-repeat bg-[left_16px_top_20px] hover:border-[#483EFF] cursor-pointer',
  },
];

export default formDataRadio;
